{"tid":1020611,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"正妹PO奶照號召！網全暴動「想壞壞」…起底竟是「最強奶媽」","createTime":"2019-02-13T17:04:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-14T12:23:29.000Z","uid":212399,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c0d5db3ce3fae7c549e7a13415125f6c93aeb9a7","tid":1020611,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T17:04:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3894/d3894446.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3894%2Fd3894446.jpg&h=ec39a22d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼原PO貼出奶照號召，希望女網友可以放上跟她一樣動作的照片。（圖／翻攝謝薇安臉書，下同）<br />\n網搜小組／綜合報導<br />\n這太母湯！一名女網友在臉書社團「爆廢公社二館」PO文說，「突然很無聊，可以蓋一個抓奶樓嗎」，立刻引起網友暴動。沒想到，也有眼尖的網友認出原PO就是「最強奶媽」，粉絲人數高達66萬人。<br />\n原來，該名女網友是知名網紅「謝薇安Vivian」，光臉書就有18萬名粉絲追蹤，IG則是突破66萬人大關；由於身材火辣加上顏質高，更曾稱霸直播界，但也在19歲時結婚、2年後生下孩子，號稱身材最好的「最強奶媽」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3894/d3894447.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3894%2Fd3894447.jpg&h=2093a2b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼沒想到原PO竟是有66萬粉絲的網紅。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3894/d3894444.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3894%2Fd3894444.jpg&h=ae1ca550&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但生下孩子後的謝薇安仍保持良好，照片一出後也讓大批網友留言，「2隻手只能抓一邊，好兇」、「抓不住，我可以幫忙扶」、「快扶老奶奶過馬路」、「真的是爆系波神...」、「感覺呼吸有點缺氧」、「4個字...有夠誇張」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3894/d3894448.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3894%2Fd3894448.jpg&h=f9b3b01f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3894/d3894445.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3894%2Fd3894445.jpg&h=62b6a5ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190213/1377362.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190213%2F1377362.htm&d=uNZXw00WsTXXX%2FAwV3JyEdey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=5f60e95f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190213/1377362.htm</a>"},{"pid":"e557ff5e74bba6a5b3a5e9c7c85d9536a518ce59","tid":1020611,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T17:05:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58d3a3bcba72422aa10c63c74e0e80d94d3c42d7","tid":1020611,"uid":143747,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T17:06:50.000Z","msg":"佢前夫幾生修導先可以同佢結婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c93a819a7a8e4b0e585210e829272d741f0281e","tid":1020611,"uid":123264,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T17:07:31.000Z","msg":"在19歲時結婚、2年後生下孩子<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n台灣mk臭雞大左唔係做雞 而係做直播主 網紅 月入十萬8萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n全民無腦用下體諗野既後果 就係大家都無得食 只能網上打j<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"442de9b7cbeda67cff748dee9ab025d4b7ae9a60","tid":1020611,"uid":124114,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T17:46:44.000Z","msg":"佢youtube段片都唔同樣"},{"pid":"b63a8e852513df8926386f72b371a7ac0594b5cb","tid":1020611,"uid":52358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T23:43:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c31a8c45c39a71c564bbe6539b6e6bf2db157391","tid":1020611,"uid":10757,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T23:44:49.000Z","msg":"又暴動"},{"pid":"23dc055219b62c945adfe5cd6458e876336c42ad","tid":1020611,"uid":12888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T23:50:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/lick.gi